 
<p>
Mississippi Republicans
<a href="https://theintercept.com/2023/04/20/mississippi-jackson-black-court/">deny the city of Jackson the right to
elect and control</a>
its own <a class=glossary href="/glossary.html#thug">thug</a> department and prosecutors.
<p>
This is an <a href="https://stallman.org/archives/2020-jan-apr.html#25_February_2020_(Undoing_justice_reform)">attempt to thwart criminal justice reform</a>,
   which would reduce the racism that "justice" systems have meted out in the past.

